name: The Bark Faces
description:
When coincidence was created, " THE BARK FACES " collection was born.
from the texture of the natural bark It is visually interpreted as a face with many expressions of emotion and story conveyed in various lines and tones in an abstract form. Let anyone who sees this picture enjoy unlimited interpretations. This collection is not based on conceptualization. But it happens in a natural flow that is unique in itself and unique.
